#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/checkout.rst:18
msgid ""
"change the :ref:`Add to Cart <ecommerce/checkout/add-to-cart>` button's "
"behavior;"
msgstr ""
"изменить поведение кнопки :ref:`Добавить в корзину <ecommerce/checkout/add-"
